com.camerontec.util.datamodel.pool

Class UnboundedPool<T extends Recyclable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.datamodel.pool.UnboundedPool<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects stored into the pool

    public final class UnboundedPool<T extends Recyclable>
extends Object
    Class implementing a simple unbounded pool of recyclable objects.

    This class is not thread safe.

    Typical pool usage is: 

     T object = pool.checkOut();
 // Use object
 // Check it back into the pool on completion.
 pool.checkIn(object);
